---
// Contacto: enlaces mailto, LinkedIn, GitHub; estilo coherente
---

<section id="contacto" class="relative scroll-mt-24 py-24 px-6">
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 opacity-50"
    style="background: var(--gradient-section-contact);"
    aria-hidden="true"
  />
  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
    <h2
      class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl"
      style="font-family: var(--font-display); background: var(--gradient-text); -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; color: transparent;"
    >
      Contacto
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-10 text-zinc-400">
      ¿Quieres trabajar juntos o charlar? Escríbeme.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="mailto:gsusete@live.com"
        class="rounded-xl bg-[var(--color-primary)] px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[var(--color-primary-dark)]"
      >
        Email
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jesussanzrocamora/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="rounded-xl border border-white/20 px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-white/10"
      >
        LinkedIn
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/ElGsusete"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="rounded-xl border border-white/20 px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-white/10"
      >
        GitHub
      </a>
      <a
        href="tel:+34634597502"
        class="rounded-xl border border-white/20 px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-white/10"
      >
        Teléfono
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
